It absorbs rays of sunlight and shoots out
energy. Its usually lurking deep beneath

Sa robustesse lui vaut parfois de travailler

Aufgrund seiner Strke arbeitet es zusammen mit

Su robustez le permite colaborar con humanos

minera.

molto robusto e per questo a volte lavora

This hardy Pokmon can often be found on
construction sites and in mines, working
alongside people and Copperajah.

Il est capable denvoyer des boules dnergie

mais il ne peut tirer que les jours ensoleills.

Seine Energiekugeln knnen einen Lastwagen

Las bolas de energa que lanza solo en das
soleados son tan potentes que pueden hacer

La potenza delle sue sfere di energia  tale da
spazzare via un camion. Tuttavia, pu spararle

Although its energy blasts can blow away
a dump truck, they have a limitation
they can only be fired when the sun is out.
